Create a PHP program to compute the sum of the digits of a number.

CODE:
<?php
// Input number (you can change this to test other values)
$number = 12345;
$original = $number;
$sum = 0;

// Loop to extract digits and add them
while ($number > 0) {
    $digit = $number % 10;     // Get the last digit
    $sum += $digit;            // Add to sum
    $number = (int)($number / 10);  // Remove the last digit
}

// Output the result
echo "The sum of the digits of $original is: $sum";
?>

ANSWER:
The sum of the digits of 12345 is: 15
